<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .error-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da 0%, #f5c6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .csrf-details {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .token-comparison {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .token-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .token-box.invalid {
            border-color: #dc3545;
            background: #f8d7da;
        }
        .token-box.valid {
            border-color: #28a745;
            background: #d4edda;
        }
        .retry-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 10px 5px;
        }
        .retry-link:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">üõ°Ô∏è‚ùå</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>CSRF token validation failed. This is a security measure to prevent cross-site request forgery attacks.</p>
        
        <div class="csrf-details">
            <h3>CSRF Validation Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Validation Time:</strong> <%= new Date().toISOString() %></p>
            
            <div class="token-comparison">
                <div class="token-box invalid">
                    <strong>Provided Token:</strong><br>
                    <code><%= provided || 'None' %></code>
                </div>
                <div class="token-box valid">
                    <strong>Expected Token:</strong><br>
                    <code><%= expected || 'Not available' %></code>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Note:</strong><br>
                CSRF tokens must match exactly and are tied to your session. Get a fresh token by visiting the login form again.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/auth/csrf-login" class="retry-link">Get New CSRF Token</a>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="retry-link">Regular Login</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>